\c 37
\s UJeremiya ufakwa entolongweni
\p
\v 1 Inkosi uZedekhiya indodana kaJosiya\x + 2 Kho. 24.17. 2 Lan. 36.10.\x* wabusa-ke esikhundleni sikaKoniya indodana kaJehoyakhimi,\x + 22. 24.\x* uNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni ambeka abe yinkosi elizweni lakoJuda.\x + 2 Kho. 24.17. 2 Lan. 36.10.\x*\x + Hez. 17.13.\x*
\v 2 Kodwa kawalalelanga, yena\x + 2 Lan. 36.12,14.\x* lenceku zakhe\x + 2 Lan. 36. 12, 14.\x* labantu belizwe, amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwakhulume ngesandla sikaJeremiya umprofethi.
\v 3 Inkosi uZedekhiya yasithuma uJehukali\x + 38.1.\x* indodana kaShelemiya\x + 38.1.\x*\x + 36.14,26; 37.13.\x* loZefaniya\x + 2 Kho. 25.18.\x* indodana kaMahaseya umpristi kuJeremiya umprofethi,\x + 35.4.\x* isithi: Ake usikhulekele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 4 UJeremiya wangena-ke waphuma phakathi kwabantu,\x + Nani 27.17.\x* ngoba babenga\add ka\add*mfaki entolongweni.\x + 32.2; 33.1.\x*
\v 5 Ibutho likaFaro laliphumile-ke eGibhithe;\x + 44.30. Hez. 17.15. 2 Lan. 36.13. 2 Kho. 24.7.\x* kwathi amaKhaladiya ayevimbezela iJerusalema esizwa amahungahunga ngabo, enyuka asuka eJerusalema.\x + 34.11,21; 37.11.\x*
\p
\v 6 Laselifika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuJeremiya umprofethi lisithi:
\v 7 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Lizakutsho njalo enkosini yakoJuda elithume kimi ukungibuza:\x + 21.2; 37.3.\x* Khangela, ibutho likaFaro eliphumele ukulisiza\x + 2.18; 37.19; 46.17. Lilo 4.17. Hez. 29.2,6,7.\x* lizabuyela elizweni lalo, iGibhithe.\x + 2.18; 37.19; 46.17. Lilo 4.17. Hez. 29.2,6,7.\x*
\v 8 AmaKhaladiya azabuya futhi,\x + 34.22.\x* alwe emelene lalumuzi,\x + 34.22.\x* awuthumbe,\x + 34.22.\x* awutshise ngomlilo.\x + 34.22.\x*\x + 21.10; 37.8.\x*
\v 9 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Lingakhohlisi imiphefumulo yenu lisithi: AmaKhaladiya isibili azasuka kithi; ngoba kawayikusuka.
\v 10 Ngoba loba lilitshaya ibutho lonke lamaKhaladiya alwa emelene lani,\x + 21.4,5.\x* kusale amadoda agwaziweyo phakathi kwabo, azasukuma, yileyo laleyo ethenteni layo, awutshise lumuzi ngomlilo.\x + 21.10; 37.8.\x*
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi ibutho lamaKhaladiya selenyukile lisuka eJerusalema ngenxa yebutho likaFaro,\x + 37 .5.\x*
\v 12 uJeremiya waphuma eJerusalema ukuya elizweni lakoBhenjamini\x + 1.1; 32.8.\x* ukuthi amonyuke phakathi kwabantu.\x + 37 .4; 39.14; 40.5,6.\x*
\v 13 Kwasekusithi esesesangweni lakoBhenjamini,\x + 20.2; 38.7. Zek. 14.10. Neh. 8.16.\x* kwakukhona lapho induna yabalindi obizo layo lalinguIrija, indodana kaShelemiya,\x + 36.14,26; 37.13.\x* indodana kaHananiya;\x + 28.1.\x* yasimbamba uJeremiya umprofethi, isithi: Uhlubukela kumaKhaladiya.\x + 21.9; 38.19; 39.9; 43.3; 52.15. Isa. 8.12.\x*
\v 14 UJeremiya wasesithi: Ngamanga; kangihlubukeli kumaKhaladiya. Kodwa kamlalelanga; ngokunjalo uIriya wambamba uJeremiya, wamletha kuziphathamandla.\x + 38.1.\x*
\v 15 Iziphathamandla zasezithukuthela ngoJeremiya, zamtshaya, zamfaka entolongweni,\x + Heb. 11.36.\x* endlini kaJonathani umbhali,\x + 37 .20.\x* ngoba zaziyenze yaba yintolongo.
\p
\v 16 UJeremiya esengene endlini yomgodi\x + 38.6,7,9; 41.7,9. Lilo 3.53. Isa. 24.22.\x* lezitokisini, uJeremiya esehlale khona insuku ezinengi,
\v 17 inkosi uZedekhiya yasithuma, yamthatha; inkosi yasimbuza endlini yayo ensitha\x + 38.16.\x* yathi: Likhona yini ilizwi elivela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni? UJeremiya wasesithi: Likhona. Wathi: Uzanikelwa esandleni senkosi yeBhabhiloni.\x + 21.7.\x*
\v 18 UJeremiya wathi futhi enkosini uZedekhiya: Ngoneni kuwe lezincekwini zakho lakulababantu ukuthi lingifake entolongweni?
\v 19 Bangaphi khathesi abaprofethi benu abaprofetha kini\x + 37 .7,8.\x* besithi: Inkosi yeBhabhiloni kayiyikufika imelane lani kumbe imelane lalelilizwe?
\v 20 Khathesi-ke, ake uzwe, nkosi yami, nkosi, kakuthi ukuncenga kwami\x + 38.26.\x* kuwe phambi kwakho, ungangibuyiseli\x + 38.26.\x* endlini kaJonathani umbhali,\x + 37 .20.\x* hlezi ngifele khona.
\v 21 Ngakho inkosi uZedekhiya yalaya ukuthi bamfake uJeremiya egumeni lentolongo,\x + 32.2.\x* lokuthi anikwe isinkwa sibe sinye ngosuku esivela esitaladini sabaphekizinkwa,\x + 1 Sam. 2.36.\x* size siphele sonke isinkwa emzini.\x + 38.9; 52.6. Lilo 2.20. Hez. 4.10,16. Isai. 3.1.\x* Ngokunjalo uJeremiya wahlala egumeni lentolongo.\x + 32.2.\x*